#. type: Plain text
#: asciidoc/demo_setup/slemicro-utm-aarch64.adoc:27
msgid ""
"For Ignition, the configuration file `config.ign` must reside in the "
"`ignition` subdirectory on the configuration media labeled `ignition`. The "
